. You can block cookies by activating the setting on your browser that allows you to refuse the setting of all or some cookies.
However, if you use your browser settings to block all cookies (including essential cookies), you may not be able to fully experience the interactive features of our Service/Website/mobile application or other related websites/mobile applications which you visit/use.
